Dialogue: 10,0:43:46.36,0:43:57.47,Song,,0,0,0,,Somewhere, I feel like I met you before. {DEEP BLUE by 福田眞純}{full lyrics found; どこかで君と出会った気がする\Nどこかで君と生きてた気がする\N悲しみを湛えたその目から涙を拭うために\Nまた会いに来たよ\N静かな風を帆にうけて滑り始めた舟\N曇りなき五月の空さえ行く先は知らない\N海の青は深い\Nいつかはきっと願いが叶うよ\Nいつかは眠らずに夢が見られるよ\N微笑みを無くした唇が愛を語るように\Nまた会いに来たよ\N静かな風を帆にうけて滑り始めた舟\N曇りなき五月の空さえ行く先は知らない\N静かな潮風に抱かれ海を見てる二人\N限りなく今が続くなら約束はいらない\N海の青は深い}
Dialogue: 10,0:43:59.27,0:44:10.38,Song,,0,0,0,,Somewhere, I feel like I lived alongside you.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:11.75,0:44:25.33,Song,,0,0,0,,To wipe the tears from your eyes, heavy with sorrow,
Dialogue: 10,0:44:25.96,0:44:30.94,Song,,0,0,0,,I've come to see you again.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:31.67,0:44:44.18,Song,,0,0,0,,A boat has begun to glide, \Nits sail filled with the gentle wind.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:44.18,0:44:57.10,Song,,0,0,0,,Even the clear May sky ahead holds unknowns.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:57.63,0:45:04.77,Song,,0,0,0,,The ocean's blue is deep.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:05.74,0:45:17.35,Song,,0,0,0,,Someday, surely, our wishes will come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:18.72,0:45:30.66,Song,,0,0,0,,Someday, we'll be able to dream without sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:31.26,0:45:44.94,Song,,0,0,0,,So that lips which have lost their smile can speak of love,
Dialogue: 10,0:45:45.38,0:45:49.65,Song,,0,0,0,,I've come to see you again.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:51.02,0:46:03.76,Song,,0,0,0,,A boat has begun to glide, \Nits sail filled with the gentle wind.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:03.76,0:46:16.57,Song,,0,0,0,,Even the clear May sky ahead holds unknowns.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:17.04,0:46:24.45,Song,,0,0,0,,The ocean's blue is deep...
